---
title: Vegetarian Bibimbap with Shaved Vegetables, Crispy Mushrooms, and Pickled Scallions
description: Bibimbap translates to “mixed rice” in Korean. This traditional Korean dish can be made with almost any ingredients, but always starts with a bed of rice and a medley of sautéed vegetables. A perfectly fried egg makes an excellent addition!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/56fa8a2efd2cb9632b8b4567.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/56fa8a2efd2cb9632b8b4567.pdf
